{"tid":1245256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"餓狗都知不咬救己之人，那些人卻為了幾兩賞銀把救命恩人送上了死囚車!!!!","createTime":"2019-06-20T08:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"162e492d5e929ee53d5088bfd807c97be098b8c6","tid":1245256,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"【歷史的眼淚】<br />\n 「老殘遊記」 作者劉鶚，八國聯軍入北京時，他也跟著到北京，發現米價暴漲，餓殍遍野，義和團則到處殺人，路上隨處是被義和團砍頭的基督教徒和被長矛刺穿肚膛的嬰兒，景象慘烈。 於是他去找佔領了糧倉的俄國佬，花重金向俄國人購下糧倉糧食分給眾多飢民，救人無數。後來八國聯軍徹了，大家也吃飽了，但有民眾密告他勾結洋人，私售政府倉粟。結果被回到京城重新作威作福的朝庭治重罪貶到新疆，後慘死於烏魯木齊市（當時叫迪化）。<br />\n<br />\n後人問道，他救的那些是人嗎？這些「人」值得救嗎？ 餓狗都知不咬救己之人，那些人卻為了幾兩賞銀把救命恩人送上了死囚車。至今這樣的人依然大有人在。。"},{"pid":"3c816aa70753867dc8c88c178aec56404e155977","tid":1245256,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQjmYtE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQjmYtE.png&h=962dd45d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2577eef6de6998d81ab04d926f3d2b4bcb502ab2","tid":1245256,"uid":104833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c816aa70753867dc8c88c178aec56404e155977","tid":1245256,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQjmYtE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQjmYtE.png&h=962dd45d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整係個背包到等狗仔查袋"},{"pid":"20590375dd1965514bea12ed8409908e48dc3d44","tid":1245256,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}